Usage: set_multi_die_analysis_mode [-help] -die_list <string> -name <string>
                                   [-report_rlrp_path_instance_list <string>]
                                   [-stacked_die_mapping <string>]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-die_list <string>                     # <die_instance_name1 die_instance_name2
                                       # ...> (string, required)
-name <string>                         # <analysis_name> (string, required)
-report_rlrp_path_instance_list <string>
                                       # <die_instance_list_file> (string, optional)
-stacked_die_mapping <string>          # <EDI_map_file1 EDI_map_file2 ...>
                                       # (string, optional)